<slide title="Installing APD">
<break/>
<image filename="ninja.gif" align="right"/>
<break lines="4"/>
<blurb fontsize="4.0em">
Install APD via PEAR
</blurb>
<example type="shell"><![CDATA[# pear install apd
% mkdir /tmp/traces]]></example>
<blurb fontsize="4.0em">
Then add the following to your %php.ini% file:
</blurb>
<example><![CDATA[zend_extension=/absolute/path/to/apd.so
apd.dumpdir=/tmp/traces]]></example>
</slide>
